data.description: 4515 Pettytown Road is a residential property located in Dale, Texas. Situated in a peaceful and picturesque setting, this property offers a serene and tranquil living experience. The house is nestled on a spacious lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities and gardening.  The property features an 1889 sqft  single-family home with a traditional design. The exterior of the house is adorned with a combination of brick and siding, giving it a classic and timeless appeal. The interior boasts an open floor plan, with extra wide hallways/doorways (ADA compliant) allowing for seamless flow between the living spaces. The living room is spacious and features large windows that look out to the large covered patio and expansive back yard .The kitchen is well-appointed with modern appliances, ample cabinet space  and counter space providing additional workspace. It is perfect for those who enjoy cooking and entertaining guests. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy dining area, ideal for family meals or intimate gatherings. The property offers three bedrooms and an office/study, providing plenty of space for a growing family or accommodating guests. The master bedroom is generously sized and includes an ensuite bathroom with a walk in shower for added convenience and privacy. The remaining bedrooms are also well-proportioned and can be utilized as guest rooms, or hobby spaces. Outside, the property offers a large backyard that presents endless possibilities. Whether you envision creating a beautiful garden oasis, setting up a play area for children, or simply enjoying outdoor activities, this space can accommodate your desires. Located in Dale, Texas, this property benefits from its proximity to various amenities and attractions. Residents can enjoy easy access to shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and recreational facilities. Additionally, the property's location provides convenient commuting options to nearby cities or towns.
